name: Artificial Intelligence (AI) Foundations
description: This collection includes fundamental skills covering concepts and principles of artificial intelligence. From technical skills such as machine learning, and large language models to common skills such as critical thinking, problem-solving, and ethics and responsibility surrounding AI. This collection covers the skills necessary to navigate an AI-powered world.
creator: https://credentialengineregistry.org/resources/ce-036d082d-d80e-41a7-99a0-2d63a4ad3a4a
author: Western Governors University
